- 3,047,846 Equity Shares were allotted to IDFC PE on account of conversion of 79,429,643 CCDs (issued or acquired, as applicable, on September 17, 2012).
- 170,377 Equity Shares were allotted to Suneeta Agrawal on account of conversion of 1,937,411 CCDs (issued on May 16, 2008).
- 85,168 Equity Shares each were allotted to Vimla Oswal and Pratik Oswal on account of conversion of 1,937,411 CCDs (issued on May 16, 2008).
- 583,566 Equity Shares were allotted to IBEF I, 314,227 Equity Shares were allotted to IBEF, 89,496 Equity Shares were allotted to Suneeta Agrawal, 44,748 Equity Shares each were allotted to Vimla Oswal and Pratik Oswal on account of conversion of 4,070,675 CCDs (issued on May 16, 2008).
